text.tspan: NextGEN Gallery Optimizer improves your site's page load speed by preventing
NextGEN's scripts & stylesheets from loading on pages without galleries.
And what's more, if you're using the original NextGEN Gallery (v1.x.xx) or the
NextCellent Gallery fork, Optimizer will intelligently fine-tune all your gallery pages too...
